{"tid":328566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣陽明山水泥泵車狂掃22車   最少4死9傷","createTime":"2017-07-19T16:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T17:14:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c92224c2a19a029448c9fbdaa7d0b2e2f6e88fcd","tid":328566,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170719/large/1500448300_99cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170719%2Flarge%2F1500448300_99cb.jpg&h=2783446f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170719/large/1500426248_4773.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170719%2Flarge%2F1500426248_4773.jpg&h=390e1cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170719/large/1500426449_0b71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170719%2Flarge%2F1500426449_0b71.jpg&h=6ba32840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170719/large/1500426450_7f74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170719%2Flarge%2F1500426450_7f74.jpg&h=19097843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣台北市陽明山仰德大道三段，今天上午8時許，發生10多部各式車連環車禍，最少造成4死9傷，消防局獲報後立即趕往救援，立即成立救護站，目前仍在救援中。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指出，事故最少涉及8部私家車、7電單車，事發時一部水泥泵車沿仰德大道落山時，疑是沒有減速圖衝紅燈時，失控撞上一部銀色私家車，釀成連環追撞，亦波及旁邊住宅。現場消息又稱，多部被撞車輛車身嚴重變形，有人被直接撞死。死者包括年約50歲的水泥泵車司機阮英貴，被直接撞倒的途人何宗益（51歲），同時還有一男一女死者的身份仍待確認。<br />\n<br />\n14：50：有私家車行車紀錄儀拍下事發煮時，前座乘客江金水跳車逃生的一幕。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tovqrA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tovqrA&d=Ow63sHXCEGGNO%2BdmMtVvnYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=accc3754\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tovqrA</a>）<br />\n<br />\n14：20：意外發生後，士林地檢署取閱現場閉路電視，外勤檢察官也正與警方鑑識人員聯繫進行相驗、履勘等事宜。檢方表示，目前的調查進度是掌握案發地點附近的閉路電視。由於案發地點近警局派出所，有多支鏡頭錄下清晰的案發過程畫面。目前的4名死者遺體都保存在醫院，其中有2人身分不詳，有待檢警以車追人，確認身分後報請相驗。<br />\n<br />\n14：10：文化大學研究生葉峻銘事發時，目睹水泥泵車向自己方向衝過來，幸好僅受輕傷。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uHkAgf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uHkAgf&d=Ow63sHXCEGGNO%2BdmMtVvnYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0bbf37ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uHkAgf</a>）<br />\n<br />\n13：06：最新閉路電視畫面曝光，片中一輛水泥泵車往下山方向，疑似煞車失靈，高速追撞前面及停在路邊的13部私家車、9部電單車。（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uGQTfD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uGQTfD&d=Ow63sHXCEGGNO%2BdmMtVvnYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=575c1524\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uGQTfD</a>）"},{"pid":"97b45acd7417fc6d53abf44321df382eb6f86924","tid":328566,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"df42b671549a19989c13924e5da4e2333b50f8ee","tid":328566,"uid":125310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"gta?"}]}